These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
Flower: daffodil, aconite, rose, begonia
1. Flower:aconite is between Flower:rose and Flower:begonia##2
2. Flower:aconite is on the left of Flower:rose##1
3. Flower:daffodil is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Flower   | daffodil | begonia | aconite | rose |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
