1. Color:blood-red is on the right of Color:mauve##1
2. Color:azure is on the right of Color:green##1
3. Color:blood-red is between Color:mauve and Color:green##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Color   | mauve | blood-red | green | azure |

